<html>
<head>
	<meta http-equiv="Content-type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
  <link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato:300,400,700' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/font-awesome.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/mdb.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
  <!-- <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/images/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon" /> -->

	<title>Seeds token sale</title>
</head>
<body onload="init({{deadline}}, {{percentageCompleted}}, {{sdsSold}}, {{askEmail}})">

  <section class="first-section">
    <div id="logo"><a href="/"><img class="logo-img" src="images/seeds-logo.png" alt="Logo"></a></div>

    {{#showProgress}}
    <div id="progressbar"></div>
    {{/showProgress}}

    <div id="clockdiv">
      <h1>{{phase}} ends in</h1>
      <div id="clockdiv-container">
        <div>
          <span class="days"></span>
          <div class="smalltext">Days</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="hours"></span>
          <div class="smalltext">Hours</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="minutes"></span>
          <div class="smalltext">Minutes</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="seconds"></span>
          <div class="smalltext">Seconds</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {{^showProgress}}
    <div id="tokenSold"></div>
    {{/showProgress}}

    <div id="discount"><p>Acquire SEEDS Tokens during the Pre-Sale phase for 25% off the listed price:</p></div>

    <!-- Button trigger modal -->
    <div class="buy-button">
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#modalContactForm">
          JOIN PRE-SALE NOW
      </button>
    </div>

    <div id="ethereum"><img src="images/ethereum.jpeg" alt="Ethereum">
      <p>Accepting Ethers: 1 SEEDS Token = {{price}} Ether</p>
    </div>

    <div class="modal fade" id="modalContactForm" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="modal-dialog cascading-modal" role="document">
          <!--Content-->
          <div class="modal-content">

              <!--Header-->
              <div class="modal-header light-blue darken-3 white-text">
                  <h4 class="title"><i class="fa fa-pencil"></i> Enter your email address</h4>
                  <button type="button" class="close waves-effect waves-light" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                      <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                  </button>
              </div>
              <!--Body-->
              <div class="modal-body mb-0">
                 <form role="form" name="modalForm" action="/contribute" method="POST">
                  <div class="md-form form-sm">
                      <i class="fa fa-envelope prefix"></i>
                      <input type="email" id="email" name="email" class="form-control">
                      <label for="email">Your email</label>
                  </div>

                  <div class="text-center mt-1-half">
                      <button class="btn btn-primary mb-2" onclick="return validateForm();">Continue <i class="fa fa-send ml-1"></i></button>
                  </div>
                </form>

              </div>
          </div>
          <!--/.Content-->
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="grey-section">
    <h3>What is Seeds?</h3>
    <p>Seeds provides a decentralized, transparent, distributed platform for submitting and fulfilling monetary needs.  When a need is uploaded, our recommendation algorithm displays that need to those within the ecosystem who will be most likely to want to fulfill it.  Needs submitted to the Seeds system can be virtually anything.  So long as itâ€™s legal and ethical, we would love to help.
    </p>

    <div id="reference-buttons">
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-green-1 btn-sm">WHITE PAPER</button>
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-green-2 btn-sm">ONE-PAGER</button>
    </div>

  </section>

  <section>
    <h3>Seeds Tokens</h3>
    <p>Seeds Tokens (SEEDS)  enable users to submit a need to be fulfilled through use of the Seeds recommendation algorithm within the Seeds ecosystem.  When a user helps to fulfill a need, s/he is entered into a lottery that awards a fixed number of tokens to all who contribute to fulfilling that need.  Winners can then submit the Seeds tokens they have won to fulfill needs of their own.
    </p>

    <div id="timeline"><img src="images/timeline.png" alt="timeline"></div>

    <p>The notional value of SEEDS is set at ~$0.04 per token. The final value will be determined by the sale</p>

    <div id="pie-chart"><img src="images/pie-chart.jpg" alt="pie-chart"></div>

    <div class="pie-chart-legend">
      <h4>Tokens allocation</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>1 Billion SEEDS issued</li>
        <li>33% For sale</li>
        <li>33% retained by Seeds</li>
        <li>33% allocated for partners to incentivise the network</li>
        <li>1% to cover token sale costs and fees</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
  <hr>
  <section>
    <h3>Ready to grow with Seeds?</h3>
    <div class="buy-button">
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#modalContactForm">
          JOIN PRE-SALE NOW
      </button>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p><b>Questions?</b> Contact us at <a href="mailto:info@playseeds.com">info@playseeds.com</a></p>
     <p><a target="_blank" href="https://www.facebook.com/seedsgives"><i class="fa fa-facebook-square fa-2x" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
     <a target="_blank" href="https://www.instagram.com/seedsgives/"><i class="fa fa-instagram fa-2x"></i></a>
     <a target="_blank" href="https://twitter.com/seedstweets"><i class="fa fa-twitter-square fa-2x"></i></a></p>
  </footer>

